    "body": "### Expected\r\n`Rename Tag` dialog should not be closed after orientation change.\r\n\r\n### Observed\r\n`Rename Tag` dialog (but not so for a `Add Tag` dialog) is closed after the device is rotated:\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/73365754/132837860-6cc04cce-8f4f-4a69-b8d5-397b2000e188.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduced\r\n1. Make sure you have at least one tag and open tags list\r\n2. Tap a tag to make `Rename Tag` dialog appear. You can keep it as it is or edit the text.\r\n3. Rotate the device ~> the dialog is closed and changes (if any) are not saved.\r\n\r\nDevice Model: Samsung A31\r\nAndroid Version: 10\r\nSimplenote Version: 2.21-rc-1\r\n",
